{"tid":913203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家樂天降肥鼠直墮餐碗 大媽嚇到叫怕怕","createTime":"2018-11-23T08:25:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T08:43:13.000Z","uid":80516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a0d5ff76cc24b5cee2f7c1fc2a288924eaddef45","tid":913203,"uid":80516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:25:29.000Z","msg":"食飯可以免費加餸當然開心，但望真啲，原來是老鼠就真係要喊出來！有網民在社交網站群組「巴打絲打 Facebook Club」貼文，指於昨日(22日)下午1時，在牛頭角樂華商場大家樂午膳時，見到她前一張檯的大媽突然驚嚇大叫，原來天降一隻肥老鼠直墮入大媽的飯碗内。<br />\n<br />\n從網友貼相中清晰可見，一隻肥老鼠置於飯碗中，老鼠疑已死掉沒有動靜，而碗中的飯已食了一大半。發文的網民形容：「個大嬸超大聲叫~~~個女經理好快走出嚟，但都比(畀)我打完卡先拎走。」<br />\n<br />\n貼文一出旋即引起網民嘩然，有網民譏諷指天降飛鼠是「神秘禮物」；亦有人指「所有大家樂都咁污糟邋遢」；有人更建議「去食環告佢」。<br />\n<br />\n大家樂回覆查詢時表示，集團對事件極為關注，已立即向有關分店了解。據悉，近日有關商場正進行防治蟲鼠工作。就是次個案，集團已即時棄置涉事餐具及進行消毒，並與商場管理處及防蟲公司商討進一步加強防禦措施。<br />\n<br />\n大家樂強調，集團有嚴謹的措施與指引，以確保所有分店的衞生都達到集團的標準；每分店亦有聘請專業承辦商，於鼠患常出沒的高危位置放置滅鼠物品及設施作防禦，並每月定期檢查鼠患情況，作防蟲滅蟲工作。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/IK1ERUY9RzpHjZ.KIgHuSA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM1/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/bd6108031cce94c94a0ec1f332e3f988\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FIK1ERUY9RzpHjZ.KIgHuSA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM1%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fbd6108031cce94c94a0ec1f332e3f988&h=1fd038f3&s={SIZE}\" />透過電腦效果，模擬了老鼠「從天而降」的情況。(巴打絲打 Facebook Club)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/AtG_P4FRTScEAh7rNnMVNg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NTU2/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/8ddcd484de92d6bf1a815068236a6437\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FAtG_P4FRTScEAh7rNnMVNg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NTU2%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F8ddcd484de92d6bf1a815068236a6437&h=ef0d9d60&s={SIZE}\" />事發地點是牛頭角樂華商場大家樂。(巴打絲打 Facebook Club)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181123/bkn-20181123103757887-1123_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181123%2Fbkn-20181123103757887-1123_00822_001.html&d=1hC2mXRqFVwtGDzsKQdeRzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=482394c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181123/bkn-20181123103757887-1123_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"db8078cb341a492a49af337e08504b3748f23831","tid":913203,"uid":59857,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:39:05.000Z","msg":"冚家炸田鼠"},{"pid":"65fd8f41bc0607229889cc00ed740280622f6370","tid":913203,"uid":838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:43:13.000Z","msg":"個電腦效果幾盞鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}